public abstract class NcoreDrawioResourceFactory<T extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject> extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.resource.impl.ResourceFactoryImpl
This factory uses DrawioResource with DrawioEObjectFactory. It injects name, description, and markers in configureSemanticElement().
